//@version=6
// Probes (pine-lint --tv, 2026-06-25). Each pair is the second decl's anchor:
//   f()/f()         -> CE10112 @ 5:2 (arity 0)
//   f(x)/f(x)       -> CE10113 @ 5:2 (same arity, untyped)
//   f(int x)/f(int y) -> CE10110 @ 5:2 (same explicit type)
// Legal (clean): f(int x)/f(string x); f(int x)/f(x); f(x)/f(x, y).
indicator("s")
f() =>
    1
f() =>
    2
plot(f())
